\par
- ACDispatch command executes but expected behavior is missing.\par
\par
Likely causes:\par
\par
- Wrong event name or argument format.\par
- ROM name mismatch with `AC_GameData.json` record.\par
- Missing event assignment in game map.\par
\par
Actions:\par
\par
1. Re-run command with known-good syntax.\par
2. Confirm ROM key in game DB.\par
3. Confirm event mapping exists and references valid effect/animation.\par
